### 创建 HTML 规则 v1（sourceId 必须是 HTML_LIST）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage6-rule-create

{
  "listSelector": ".article-item",
  "linkSelector": "a.title",
  "titleSelector": "h1",
  "contentSelector": "article .content",
  "authorSelector": ".author",
  "publishTimeSelector": "time",
  "datePattern": "",
  "removeSelectors": ".advertisement\n.related-links\nscript\niframe",
  "enabled": true
}

> {%
client.test("规则版本创建成功", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 201, "预期 HTTP 201");
  client.assert(response.body.data.version >= 1, "规则版本必须大于等于 1");
});
%}

### 查询规则版本
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules
Accept: application/json

### 查询当前规则
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules/active
Accept: application/json

### 无入库规则测试
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules/test
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage6-rule-test

### 激活历史版本
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules/1/active
Accept: application/json

### 参数错误：缺少必要选择器
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{"listSelector":"","linkSelector":"","titleSelector":"","contentSelector":"","enabled":true}

### 记录不存在
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/999999/rules
Accept: application/json
